som ti za to vďačná.

78
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,250
Stlač to poriadne.

79
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,610
Prečo si taká milá?

80
00:05:29,610 --> 00:05:32,080
Pretože by som mohol zomrieť?

81
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:34,270
