Hlupáčik. Už som ti odpovedala.

112
00:08:17,330 --> 00:08:19,320
Chýbaš mi.

113
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:34,780
Jedol si?

114
00:08:35,810 --> 00:08:38,060
Chýbaš mi.

115
00:08:45,100 --> 00:08:47,020
Viem.

116
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,950
Plačeš?

117
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:59,790
Mimochodom, spomínaš si?

118
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:02,160
Keď sme sa druhýkrát stretli,

119
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:04,900
mala som na sebe biele šaty.

120
00:09:04,900 --> 00:09:06,990
Spýtal si sa ma,

121
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:09,490
či mojim cieľom je vyzerať
ako duch panny.

122
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:13,870
<i>Keď o tom premýšľam,</i>

123
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:16,450
